{"id":147647,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/译文精选：“鼠居”在北京的人们（图辑）/","date":"2011-04-25T23:25:02Z","modified":"2011-04-25T23:25:02Z","title":"译文精选：“鼠居”在北京的人们（图辑）","content":"<p>原作者：<br />\n来源<a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/slideshow/2011/04/24/magazine/beijing-basements.html\">The ‘Mouse People’ of Beijing &#8211; Slide Show &#8211; NYTimescom</a><br />\n译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/220316\">wingsu</a></p>\n<p>1  在北京的地下防空洞里，现在也许聚居着数以万计的民工。21岁的刘静（音）是个修脚师，现在她和另外两个同事一起住在由防空洞改造的地下室里。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/25/20110425160400_90188.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>2  宋志飞（音）和李国强（音）是学武术的学生，他们在老师的地下训练室里练拳。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/25/20110425160437_39518.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>3 、 23岁的何兵（音）次日要参加保险推销员的面试，他正在试穿一条借来的领带和一件新衬衫。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/25/20110425160402_79360.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>4 、30岁的杜威（音）在由地下防空洞改造的房子的公用卫生间里。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/25/20110425160417_48300.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>5、25岁的冯涛是个发型设计师，他和同龄的女友庄秋丽一起住在北京东部一座公寓的地下室二层。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/25/20110425160420_43622.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>6、北京西部地下防空洞里的一间经理室（这是复式房里最大的一间）。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/25/20110425160454_26440.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>7、地下室入口边的锁风通行道的墙上写着“租房”。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/25/20110425160440_63919.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/220316/189820#newComment\">添加新评论</a></p>\n<p><strong><br />\n</strong></p>\n<form action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\" method=\"POST\"> 定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n<input maxlength=\"64\" name=\"EMAIL\" size=\"25\" type=\"text\" /></p>\n<p><input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\" /> <input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\" /> <input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\" /> </form>\n","author":1,"categories":[13770,20534],"tags":[17141,16347]}